NXEngine for DC
===============

About
-----

A complete open-source clone/rewrite of the masterpiece jump-and-run platformer Doukutsu Monogatari (also known as Cave Story).

<http://nxengine.sourceforge.net>


Installation
------------

download Cave Story 1.0.0.6 with Aeon Genesis English translation
(e.g cavestory.zip) and extract it

download nxextract.zip and extract it
This contain these files.
1. nxextract.exe
2. smalfont.bmp
3. sprites.sif
4. tilekey.dat

and SDL.dll if you havn't

put above files to doukutsu data directorty(e.g cavestory)

change the directory 
and open nxextract.exe

press key

press key

you get "Done" message

press key to close the programme.

you don't need nxextract.exe (and SDL.dll)

put 1ST_READ.BIN 

Now you can burn CD

CD structure
ROOT
|
1ST_READ.BIN
data/
drum.pcm
endpic/
org/
pxt/
smalfont.bmp
sndcache.pcm
sprite.sif
stage.dat
tilekey.dat
wavetable.dat

Controls
--------

Dreamcast controller:
D-pad:	left,right,down,up
A:		jump
B:		fire
X:		inventory
Y:		mapsystem
L trigger:	prev wepon
R trigger:	next wepon
Start:	F3

Dreamcast keyboard:
allow, f1 - f12, esc, 0 - 9, a - z

